<div style="padding:30px 20px; color:#333;">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>An eligibility application for <%= organizationName %> has been submitted and requires your signature as Head Authorized Official.</p>
    <p>Please sign in to American Surplus and complete the application signature:</p>
    <p>
        <a href="<%= applicationUrl %>" style="display:inline-block; padding:10px 20px; background-color:#007BFF; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:5px;">
            Review and sign application
        </a>
    </p>
    <p>You must verify your email address before signing if you have not already done so.</p>
    <p>Thanks,<br />American Surplus</p>
</div>
